creator: Ruben Sousa
descriptionHtml:
The unofficial app for you to check news/stats/game status of Apex Legends and everything is in your hand. Quickly check your profile stats or the current game status.
Features include:
- Latest news feed from the game;
- Search and check player profile stats (level, ranks, match history...);
- Player base counts;
- Map rotations;
- Online services status.

*Important Disclaimer:* Data is NOT provided by the app developer or may not be completely accurate, since it depends on unofficial APIs.
descriptionShort: The unofficial app for you to check news/stats/game status of Apex Legends!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: - Added resources to correctly display new map rotations, due to the latest game update.
